      <title>莫迪耗资 60 亿美元的潜艇建造计划因海上试验而搁浅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/modi-s-6-billion-submarine-building-plan-stalls-after-sea-tests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于承包商抱怨海上测试期间没有遵循正确的程序，印度耗资 60 亿美元的潜艇建造计划陷入停滞，从而推迟了印度海军随着中国扩大在印度洋的存在而增强其能力的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/modi-s-6-billion-submarine-building-plan-stalls-after-sea-tests</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 07:10:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国军舰罕见访问柬埔寨基地 成为争端焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/us-warship-makes-rare-visit-to-cambodia-base-at-center-of-feud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，自 2019 年柬埔寨与中国签署协议允许中国在该国建立永久立足点以来，美国将首次派遣军舰访问该国海军基地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/us-warship-makes-rare-visit-to-cambodia-base-at-center-of-feud</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 07:04:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非和莱索托之间的争端使水利项目面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/south-africa-lesotho-row-puts-water-project-at-risk-bd-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《商业日报》援引法庭文件和其他资料报道称，外交争端可能会进一步推迟莱索托数十亿美元的项目建设，而该项目是为了避免南非的水危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/south-africa-lesotho-row-puts-water-project-at-risk-bd-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 05:39:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾审议法律变更，使宣布戒严更加困难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/taiwan-reviews-legal-change-making-martial-law-harder-to-declare</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾立法机构即将审议一项拟议的法律修正案，该修正案将使总统宣布戒严变得更加困难。在本月初韩国令人震惊的紧急状态宣言之后，反对党国民党议员支持这一修正案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/taiwan-reviews-legal-change-making-martial-law-harder-to-declare</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 04:52:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>距离戒严还有五分钟：尹永哲的突然举动震惊内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/five-minutes-to-martial-law-yoon-stunned-cabinet-with-snap-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国正在等待反对派于周六再次推动弹劾总统尹锡烈，有关其宣布戒严前后几个小时发生的事情的更多细节正在浮出水面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/five-minutes-to-martial-law-yoon-stunned-cabinet-with-snap-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 02:01:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国对尹永哲的支持率在关键弹劾投票前跌至历史最低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/south-korean-leader-s-support-hits-record-low-after-martial-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈试图捍卫其戒严令并抵制通过弹劾将其赶下台的努力，其支持率跌至就任以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/south-korean-leader-s-support-hits-record-low-after-martial-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 01:12:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚反对党公布 2110 亿美元核计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/australia-s-opposition-reveals-211-billion-nuclear-power-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管澳大利亚顶尖科学家表示风能和太阳能等可再生能源更具成本效益，但澳大利亚主要反对党仍提出一项耗资 3,310 亿澳元（2,110 亿美元）的计划，计划在短短十年内打造一个由纳税人资助的核电产业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/australia-s-opposition-reveals-211-billion-nuclear-power-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 00:11:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本企业信心保持乐观，符合日本央行观点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/japan-s-large-manufacturers-sentiment-strengthens-ahead-of-boj</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本大型企业的信心依然乐观，与日本央行下周政策会议前的观点基本一致，分析师对于是否会加息意见不一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/japan-s-large-manufacturers-sentiment-strengthens-ahead-of-boj</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 00:04:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝索斯计划访问特朗普，亚马逊向其就职典礼捐款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/bezos-to-visit-president-elect-next-week-trump-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司发言人表示，该公司将向当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的就职基金捐赠 100 万美元，与 Meta Platforms Inc. 一起为庆祝活动做出贡献，因为科技公司希望与政府建立积极的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/bezos-to-visit-president-elect-next-week-trump-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 15:18:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索马里地区计划对伊斯兰国发动新攻势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/oil-rich-somali-region-plans-new-offensive-against-islamic-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[半自治区邦特兰正计划发动新一轮攻势，打击索马里北部山区日益壮大的伊斯兰国叛乱势力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/oil-rich-somali-region-plans-new-offensive-against-islamic-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 06:44:51 GMT</pubDate>
